Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.54,0:00:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-一座塔  -我需要在春天之前完工\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-A tower? -I need it completed by spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.25,0:00:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您有没有考虑过 在外族中寻求合作伙伴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you considered seeking partners outside the confines of our own race?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.58,0:00:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我说说你国王的提议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me about your King's proposal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来决定要不要呈报给我父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so I can present it to my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.62,0:00:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他有所隐瞒 我是能感受到的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd sense it if he were hiding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.75,0:00:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许他感受到了有所隐瞒的人是你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps he sensed that it was you who was hiding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.75,0:00:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努门诺尔岛国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Island Kingdom of Númenor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.58,0:00:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在考虑推迟参加海洋试炼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was thinking I might defer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.20,0:00:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等海洋试炼开始 那艘船启航时 你必须在船上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When the Sea Trial begins and that ship launches, you will be on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.04,0:00:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想惹麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't want any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.33,0:00:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是南方大地的地图\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is a map of the Southlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.12,0:00:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它不仅提及了一个地点 还讲述了一项计划\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It speaks not only of a place, but a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.45,0:00:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们将建立自己的领地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To create a realm of their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.20,0:00:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南方大地正处于严重危险之中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then the Southlands are in grave danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.25,0:00:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果索隆真的已经卷土重来 那么南方大地只会是个开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If Sauron has indeed returned, the Southlands are but the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:00:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们这里有谁想活命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If there are any of you here who want to live...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:01:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们明天日出时刻就一起前往精灵塔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...we make for the Elven tower at first light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.12,0:01:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他带给阿达尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bring him to Adar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.95,0:01:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说古时候 索隆有很多个名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Adar! Sauron was said to have many names in days of old.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.62,0:01:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许这就是其中一个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps this is one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.12,0:01:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的同胞没有国王 因为你就是国王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your people have no king, for you are him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.37,0:01:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一起去中洲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come with me to Middle-earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.12,0:01:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有军队\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're still short an army.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.62,0:01:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些马上就将改变\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is all about to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.58,0:02:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}指环王：力量之戒\N第一季第四集
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.58,0:02:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21}本WEB版外挂字幕由  {\c&H9B30FF&}风吹来的那片云{\c&HFFFFFF&}  双语合并
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这座王宫 我们每天 都会齐聚一堂 共同规划岛屿的未来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In this court, we gather daily to hammer out our island's future.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在“祝福新生儿”仪式中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But at the Blessing of the Children,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.20,0:03:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们欢聚一堂 共庆新生 他们长大后将见证这座岛屿的未来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we gather to welcome those who will live that future.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子就像冲破海面波涛的朝阳 拥有无限的未来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One as boundless as a sunrise over the rolling sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.08,0:03:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给她取了什么名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What name have you chosen for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳内尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alinel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳内尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alinel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿你能够拥有努门诺尔的力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}May Númenor's strength arise in thee.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.45,0:03:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿她的智慧指引你的脚步…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Her wisdom guide thy steps...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时我们的岛屿也需要“活动”一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sometimes our island just needs a stretch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是美好的一天 摄政女王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-It is a perfect day, Queen Regent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.62,0:04:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要先处理什么事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What business would you begin with?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.66,0:04:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她把那个精灵传唤到了王宫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She summoned the Elf to court.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是今早上的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精灵的同伴动手打了四个公会成员 而弥瑞尔却请她喝茶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elf's mate attacks four guildsmen, and Míriel has her up for tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.83,0:04:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能传唤精灵就是为了要惩罚她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Probably she called the Elf in to punish her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.08,0:04:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有可能是向她讨教\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Or to ask her for orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精灵在我们的女王耳边扇阴风点鬼火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And while the Elf whispers poison in our Queen's ear,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.50,0:05:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来替我们说话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-who's speaking for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Chancellor! Chancellor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替我向她问好 好吗 你小声点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Send her my regards, will you? Keep your voice down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.45,0:05:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要来一份吗 先生 来一份吧 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Would you like one, sir? Come on, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.91,0:05:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道您在忙很重要的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't realize you were in the middle of something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.70,0:05:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Chancellor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治国之道就是要事无巨细\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Statecraft is the art of attending to small matters
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.58,0:05:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事必躬亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as diligently as grand ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.16,0:05:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为你现在已经学到这一点了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should like to think you'd learned that by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在想办法学着变聪明点儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was only trying to be clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.37,0:05:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野心不大的人才会只顾一味地变聪明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cleverness is for men of small ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.87,0:05:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我更希望你能有智慧 儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd much rather it if you were wise, my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.75,0:05:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说吧 出什么问题了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, what seems to be the trouble, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在我们眼皮底下挑事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We may have a bit of a squall on our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精灵的船悍然停在我们的海岸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elf ships on our shore?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精灵工匠抢走你们的商业贸易\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elf workers taking your trades?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.95,0:05:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些工匠不需要睡觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Workers who don't sleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.12,0:06:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会疲倦 也不会变老\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}don't tire, don't age.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.58,0:06:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.41,0:06:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我说 女王要么是瞎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I say, the Queen's either blind
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要么就是精灵的舔狗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or an Elf lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟她父亲一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Just like her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-精灵的舔狗  -精灵的舔狗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Elf lover! -Elf lover!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-精灵的舔狗  -精灵的舔狗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elf lover!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.79,0:06:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精灵的舔狗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elf lover! Elf lover!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.66,0:06:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那个精灵现在就站在这里 她看到的会是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if the Elf were here now, what would she see?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是努门诺尔的铁血男儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Men of Númenor,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是一群只会哭闹的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or a gaggle of mewling children?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是伊甸人的儿女\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We are sons and daughters of the Edain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是国王埃尔洛斯塔尔明雅图尔的后代 他曾亲自率军打败魔苟斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of Elros Tar-Minyatur, whose host conquered Morgoth himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.58,0:06:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而现在区区一个 坐船逃难的精灵就能威胁到我们吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But now one Elf, a castaway, could threaten us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们所有人 低头看看自己佩戴的公会徽章\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look down, each of you, at the guild crests you bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是传承自力量强大之手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The heritage of mighty hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是伟大的祖先用双手竖起了海堤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of men who laid the Sea Wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:07:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建造了象征我们文明胜利的 阿美尼洛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who raised Armenelos, triumph of our civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.37,0:07:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在 区区一个精灵就能威胁我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But now, one Elf could threaten us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友们…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.16,0:07:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Trust in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.91,0:07:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看我手上的老茧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For by the calluses on my hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.54,0:07:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发誓精灵之手 永远无法夺走努门诺尔王国的船舵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I swear that Elven hands will never take Númenor's helm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.75,0:07:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努门诺尔王国将一如既往地属于人类\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She will remain, as always, a kingdom of Men.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.41,0:07:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我请大家喝一杯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Drinks all around!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他熟知这座城市里每个人的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Isn't a name in this city he doesn't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.29,0:08:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总能说服人群改变想法 几乎所有人都欠他人情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a crowd he can't turn, a favor he isn't owed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.45,0:08:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太了不起了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,0:08:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来想说“太让人不爽了”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was going to say "infuriating."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.37,0:08:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这酒产自美尼尔塔玛的葡萄园\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From vineyards near the Meneltarma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该能让你忘记烦恼 反正人们是这么说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Supposed to make you forget your troubles. Or so they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.87,0:08:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些甜蜜的烦恼都是我自己争取来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My troubles have been too hard-won.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是那个新来的学徒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You must be the new apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫凯门 你叫…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm Kemen. And your name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃雅瑞恩 赶紧交平面图\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, E?rien. Plans, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你惹恼我了 精灵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You vex me, Elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.45,0:09:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你以礼相待\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I welcome you as a guest,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你却跑到我们乡下去偷古老的卷轴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you gallop off to our countryside to steal ancient scrolls
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.20,0:09:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与此同时 你那位来自中洲南方的 同伴还打了我们的公民\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}whilst your Southlander companion assaults our citizenry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.66,0:09:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的暴脾气可以理解 毕竟他的人民正在死去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He is understandably quick to temper. His people are dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“他的人民”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"His people"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你关在地牢里的那一位 并不是普通的闹事者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I believe the man you hold in your dungeons is no common brawler,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是流亡在外 下落不明的南方大地王位继承人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but the lost heir in exile to the throne of the Southlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那看来埃兰迪尔是一位东夷皇帝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I suppose Elendil here is a Rh?nic emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实也就是个小领主\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just a petty lord, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.66,0:09:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的人民散落各地 群龙无首\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His people are scattered. Leaderless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.45,0:09:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有了你的支持 他们可能会 团结在他的旗帜之下 共同战斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But with your backing they might unite behind his banner. And fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.62,0:09:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的“支持”是什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you mean "backing"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索隆曾经是你们人类的敌人 也是我们精灵的敌人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sauron was once your people's enemy, as much as mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我请求您完成这件未竟之事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I call on you to finish the task left undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.12,0:09:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重建努门诺尔和精灵之间的联盟…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To reforge the alliance between Númenor and Elves...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.08,0:09:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我并肩作战 拯救南方大地的人类\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And fight with me, to save the men of the Southlands
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避免索隆将他们的土地据为己有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}before Sauron claims their lands for his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.58,0:10:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个王宫之中 我们经常听到许多提案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In this court we hear many proposals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.16,0:10:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的提案是几周来 我听过最令人惊讶、最具野心的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I dare say yours is the most surprising and ambitious I've heard in weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.75,0:10:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 努门诺尔已经 选择了另一条道路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nevertheless, Númenor has chosen another path.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非所有人都是如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not all Númenor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.66,0:10:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个来自南方大地的人 不管 他是国王还是木匠 都将面临审判\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}King or carpenter, the Southlander will face judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次会面结束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This audience is ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我别无选择了 只能要求另一场会面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then I have little choice, but to ask for another.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要求与努门诺尔真正的统治者会面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One with Númenor's true ruler.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是你的父亲 国王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your father, the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.37,0:10:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不应该说起你根本不了解的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should not speak of matters you do not understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.12,0:10:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞尔 菲纳芬之女\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel, daughter of Finarfin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.91,0:10:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该靠边站\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you should stand aside,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.16,0:11:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我才能 向真正有权答复我的人提出提案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that I might present my proposal to one who holds the authority to answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞尔女士 够了…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lady Galadriel, that is quite enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你凭什么说这番话 精灵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And with what authority do you speak, Elf?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.75,0:11:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭你的人民\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That of your people?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.79,0:11:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说你就是个坐船逃难的精灵 想在风暴中抓住救命稻草\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or are you a castaway, grasping for a handhold in a tempest?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.37,0:11:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我内心就有一股强烈的风暴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is a tempest in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.25,0:11:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它把我刮到这座岛上一定是有原因的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It swept me to this island for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.33,0:11:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你无法平息这股风暴 摄政王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And it will not be quelled by you, Regent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜猜看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为在酒馆斗殴进来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tavern brawl?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.12,0:11:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为发表煽动性言论\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sedition.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.83,0:11:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就快要成功了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've nearly made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.25,0:11:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再过几天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In a few more days,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.75,0:11:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能很荣幸地 称呼你们所有人为船员了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll have the pleasure of calling all of you shipmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.08,0:11:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快拉 学员们 拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pull now, cadets! Pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.83,0:12:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊熙尔杜…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Isildur...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.45,0:12:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快拉 学员们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pull now, cadets!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.33,0:12:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.87,0:12:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绳索\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.91,0:12:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好好解释一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Explain yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.25,0:12:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长官 这肯定搞错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, no, there must be some sort of mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.95,0:12:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错 航海官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was my fault, Sea-master.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.66,0:12:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我放手了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I let it slip.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.87,0:12:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那条升降索 我见过你成功收放不下一百次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've seen you ease that halyard proper a hundred times.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才是故意的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That was deliberate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被踢出海上卫队了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're off the Sea Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们仨全部淘汰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All three of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.66,0:13:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“西部” “真正的努门诺尔”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"The West"? "The real Númenor"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.62,0:13:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你哥常挂在嘴边的那些胡话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That garbage your brother used to spew, again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为航海官只会开除我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought the sail-master would only dismiss me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对不起  你刚刚毁了我们俩的一生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're sorry? You just set our whole lives on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜壶在哪里 我要吐了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's that chamber pot? I think I'm gonna be sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.66,0:13:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去和我爸谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will speak to my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-给你们俩恢复原职 -用不着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Convince him to see that you're both reinstated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.75,0:13:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托你的福给踢出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Leave it to you to get kicked out of something
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更别说这个机会 本来也不是你自己赢来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you never earned in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-维蓝迪尔… -不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Valandil... -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自打我能握住船桨起 我就一直想登上那艘船\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Since I was big enough to hold an oar, I wanted on that boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做好了一切准备 拼尽全力去争取 而你又做了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did everything I was supposed to do to earn it. And what did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了念叨你死去的母亲 你还做过什么?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What have you ever done but brood and blabber about your dead mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.62,0:13:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 够了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Stop it! Stop it! Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是伊熙尔杜标志性的转身走人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, same old Isil walking away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.95,0:13:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊熙尔杜 你要去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Isil! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.25,0:13:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是去是留 有什么关系吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Going, staying, what does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.00,0:14:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他才是真正的问题所在 这是无可争辩的事实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The real problem is him. And that's not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马格罗特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Magrot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.54,0:14:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿达尔…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Adar...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.45,0:15:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿达尔…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Adar...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无惧赴死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nampak uglursha.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.70,0:16:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无惧赴死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nampak uglursha.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.58,0:16:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的出生地在哪里…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where were you born,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.12,0:16:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士兵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.83,0:16:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝烈瑞安德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Beleriand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在河口附近\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}By the mouth of the river?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经去过那条河\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I went down that river once...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.25,0:17:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时我还年轻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.91,0:17:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.45,0:17:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河岸上开满了鼠尾草花\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The banks were covered in sage blossoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.00,0:17:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绵延好几英里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Miles of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.12,0:17:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么奥克称呼你为父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why do the Orcs call you Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.16,0:17:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听过很多谎言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have been told many lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.00,0:17:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的谎言编得很真\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some run so deep,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.08,0:18:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就连岩石和树根都会相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}even the rocks and roots now believe them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.37,0:18:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要揭开谎言…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To untangle it all...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几乎需要创造一个新世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}would all but require the creation of a new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.87,0:18:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是只有神才能做到的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But that is something only the gods can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是神 起码…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I am no god. At least...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时还不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.20,0:18:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是什么东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.33,0:18:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去找那些在旧瞭望塔避难的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go to the Men who have taken refuge in the old watchtower.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.54,0:18:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给他们捎个口信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Deliver to them a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么口信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What message?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兵营已经满了 大家尽可能找地方扎营\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The barracks are already full. Try and make camp where you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.08,0:19:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这些人是从哪来的  -罗尔巴德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Where's this lot from? -Iorbad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.20,0:19:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么从这儿到欧洛朱因 所有村庄的人都到齐了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That makes it every village from here to Orodruin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.79,0:19:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's the rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.87,0:19:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下这些了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.87,0:19:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还得减少口粮配额\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll have to cut rations again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.58,0:19:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能减我的配额\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not cutting my rations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是谁给你的决定权  -当然是每个决定来这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who gave you the right to decide?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.75,0:19:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这座瓦尔德雷格瞭望塔的人 其中也包括你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everyone who decided to come to this tower, Waldreg. Including you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们吃什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What will we eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我们会想出办法的 -什么办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-We'll find a way. -How?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我不知道 -你能知道才怪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I don't know. -Huh. Plain enough to see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去瓦尔德雷格的地窖看看怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about Waldreg's root cellar?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们派一个小队进镇里去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We send a small party into town.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.79,0:20:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等白天奥克数量比较少时 悄悄行动 把能拿走的东西迅速拿走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}By day, when the Orcs are fewer, grab what we can, quick and quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.00,0:20:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥克根本不会知道我们去过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They'll never even know we were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你准备忽悠哪些倒霉蛋去干这事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What poor sod will you rope into that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.91,0:20:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果其他人不愿意去 我自己去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll do it, if nobody else will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.29,0:20:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not going down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.75,0:20:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们先再次上山觅食 去召集猎人吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll forage the hills again first. Gather the hunters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.95,0:20:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们去捕什么 几只兔子吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And what will they hunt? A few rabbits?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.45,0:20:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只够我们撑一天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That'll feed us a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.70,0:20:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撑过一天是一天 能多撑一天就应该心存感激\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then it's another day. And let us be grateful for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.54,0:20:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受够了这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sick and tired
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.70,0:20:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着一切支离破碎却无动于衷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of watching everything go to tatters and not doing anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我们已经在尽力而为了 -但我没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-We are doing everything we can. -Well, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希奥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Theo. Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要么帮我 要么就是给我找麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can either help me or you can make it harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.41,0:20:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才就不应该听你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should never have let you talk me into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.37,0:21:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm heading back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.37,0:21:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么怂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't be such a soft-belly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.50,0:21:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗恩 那边有小酒馆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rowan, the tavern.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.50,0:21:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不进去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not going in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.33,0:21:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里边可能有更多的食物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-There might be more food.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.91,0:21:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 那个地方已经荒废了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, this place is deserted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 那我去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.66,0:22:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗恩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rowan?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.58,0:23:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,童子血\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Young blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.50,0:23:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这你是从哪儿弄来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where'd you get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.08,0:23:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.20,0:23:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我找到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oi! I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.08,0:23:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到了 是个小男孩  他手上有剑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I found it! It's a boy! He has the hilt!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.04,0:23:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩 他在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A boy? Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.79,0:23:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就躲在这附近\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-He's hiding here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.33,0:23:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 去向父亲大人报告\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You! Send word to Lord-father.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.04,0:24:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人 散开搜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rest of you, fan out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.12,0:24:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到他 谁也别想睡觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nobody sleeps till he's found.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.50,0:24:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Got ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.20,0:24:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精灵和矮人通力合作 真了不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elves and Dwarves working together. Remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.04,0:24:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都被你言中了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is everything you said it would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.70,0:25:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.00,0:25:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 只是…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing. Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.33,0:25:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你站在那里 有那么一瞬间 像极了你父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For a moment, standing there, you were the very image of your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.08,0:25:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我都不知道你见过我父亲 -当然了 见过很多次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wasn't aware you'd ever met him. Of course, many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.75,0:25:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他拥有远眺未来的能力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He had that way of seeing far off.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.16,0:25:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗 我记得有一次 他对我说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you know, I remember once, he said to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.54,0:25:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“总有一天 我的未来都将掌握在我儿子手中”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}one day, my future would be in his son's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.41,0:25:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说得很随意 就好像是在说明天要下雨似的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He said it quite casually, as if one might speak of tomorrow's rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.79,0:25:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我却…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I've... I've...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.41,0:25:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都忘了 直到…直到此时此刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd forgotten that until... Till this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.41,0:25:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是很奇怪吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Isn't that odd?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.37,0:25:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下 您今天似乎很不安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You seem unsettled today, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.87,0:25:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事情在困扰您\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-What troubles you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.25,0:25:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我向自己保证过绝不提起 他毕竟是你朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I promised myself I wouldn't mention it. He's your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.95,0:25:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Durin.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.50,0:26:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要么是在躲避我 要么是在隐瞒什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Either he's avoiding me or he's... he's hiding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.37,0:26:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问过他出工的团队了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you try asking his work teams?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.50,0:26:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,19个矮人我都问了 他们全都在找借口推辞我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All nineteen of them. They keep putting me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.45,0:26:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我感觉近乎可疑了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One would almost think it suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.54,0:26:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在暗示 都林给自己找了个小女朋友吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you suggesting Durin's got himself a wee girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.87,0:26:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-夫人 你是都林的唯一 -我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-There is none other than you, milady. -I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.00,0:26:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会要他啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Who'd have him?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.37,0:26:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老富婆 亲石头 抛光宝石 把金打磨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rich crone, kiss the stone Polish your gems and gold
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.08,0:26:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别闹了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Ow! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.04,0:26:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格尔达 别打你弟弟了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gerda, stop hitting your brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.83,0:26:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我们在玩敲门游戏 -好吧 别闹了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're playing the knocking game. -Well, knock it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.58,0:26:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去金色阶梯找过了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you tried the Golden Stairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.33,0:26:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者三门守卫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or the Three-door Guard?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.29,0:26:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.66,0:26:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些熊孩子把我的脑子都喊糊涂了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These wee'ns are turning my mind to mush.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.00,0:27:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他今天去石英矿坑采矿去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was off to mine Quartz Chasm today.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.91,0:27:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗 迪莎 没有什么秘密值得用欺骗来掩饰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, Disa, there is no secret worth concealing with deception.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.37,0:27:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在我家指着鼻子说矮人不诚实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Calling a Dwarf dishonest in her own home?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.08,0:27:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话火药味颇浓啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's a recipe for strong gravy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.50,0:27:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果都林在采石英矿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If Durin is mining quartz,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.16,0:27:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他为什么不带着他的凿斧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}why would he leave without taking his chiseling axe?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.00,0:27:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你为什么 这么早就准备他爱吃的菜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And why would you prepare his favorite meal
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.41,0:27:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他需要两天时间才能下降到那个矿坑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if he's gone to a chasm that takes two full days to descend to?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.91,0:27:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老富婆 亲石头 抛光宝石…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rich crone, kiss the stone Polish your gems and gold
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.54,0:27:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格尔达 我警告你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gerda, I'm warning you!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.12,0:27:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都林没有带斧头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Durin didn't bring his axe
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.66,0:27:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为他开采的石英不需要凿 而是需要撬的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because the quartz he's mining isn't chiseled. It is pried.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.16,0:27:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在做鼹鼠尾炖菜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am making mole-tail stew
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.79,0:27:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为赶在他回家之前 做好这道菜还需要花上一些时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because it needs a wee while to set before he's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.62,0:27:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然对于像你这样的外族来说 下降到矿坑可能需要几天时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And while it may take several days for an outsider, such as you,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.70,0:27:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但像我丈夫一样的矮人攀登者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dwarven climbers like my husband
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.75,0:28:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以在几个小时内就下降到石英矿坑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}can make the descent to Quartz Chasm in just a few hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.45,0:28:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还有什么想问的吗 亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was there anything else you wanted to ask about, dearie?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.37,0:28:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.70,0:28:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.04,0:28:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石英矿坑 编得不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Quartz Chasm. Not bad. Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.75,0:28:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就盼着他信了我 那个精灵可真不容易骗啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just hope he believed me. He's not easily taken in, that Elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.33,0:28:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定不容易骗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Certainly not.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.79,0:28:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸运的是 我未来的女王居然能把精灵忽悠信了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lucky my future queen could convince a water rat to wear a mink coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.12,0:28:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又多了一个娶了你的好处 幸亏当年没娶马吉德鲁斯特博林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One more reason to count my blessings I married you, not Margid Rustborin.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.58,0:28:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么其他好处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And what are the other reasons?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.00,0:28:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回头告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll tell you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.62,0:28:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静 我们最好还是小声点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hush now. We better keep our pipes down.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.08,0:28:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的旧矿开采进展顺利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're making good progress in the old mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.25,0:28:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我确保他被护送离开…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I made sure he was escorted out...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.66,0:29:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镜影湖下面的旧矿场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The old mine below the Mirrormere.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.00,0:29:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精灵 你迷路了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You lost, Elf?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.08,0:29:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 我很清楚自己要去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I know exactly where I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.08,0:29:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.95,0:30:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老富婆 亲石头 抛光宝石 把金打磨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Rich crone, kiss the stone. Polish your gems and gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.08,0:31:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.12,0:31:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Durin?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.25,0:31:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精灵 你是来监视我的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Came to spy on me, Elf? -Hardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.12,0:31:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是 这是什么地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.20,0:31:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真指望我相信你什么都不知道吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You really expect me to believe you do not know?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.20,0:31:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是他派你来的真正原因吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That this was not the true reason he sent you here to begin with?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.20,0:31:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们想要据为己有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want it for yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.16,0:31:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都林 想要什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Durin, want what?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.41,0:31:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不在乎那个洞穴里有什么东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I care nothing for whatever is in that chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.75,0:31:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只在乎你 在乎这份友谊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do care for you, for this friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.41,0:31:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而秘密是会阻碍友谊的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And secrets do not become it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.12,0:31:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么大场面是在干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is the meaning of all this? Mm?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.33,0:31:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得发誓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need your oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.50,0:31:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向山起誓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hand to mountain,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.16,0:31:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你永远不会将我要告诉你的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you'll never breathe so much as a whisper
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.08,0:31:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉其他生灵 哪怕是轻声细语也不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of what I'm about to tell you to another living soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.54,0:32:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矮人的记仇能力比精灵的记忆力还强\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dwarven anger outlives even Elven memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.20,0:32:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你违背誓言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Break your promise,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.70,0:32:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这块石头的力量 必将令你和你的亲人陷入悲伤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the power of this stone will doom you and your kin to sorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.54,0:32:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直至你们活在中洲的最后一天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to your last day on this Middle-earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.04,0:32:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你敢这样发誓吗 埃尔隆德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you swear it, Elrond?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.58,0:32:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以我父亲 水手埃雅仁迪尔的名义起誓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I swear on the memory of my father, E?rendil the Mariner.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.16,0:32:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里告诉我的任何事情 都将止于我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anything you tell me here will end in my ears alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.62,0:32:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪莎在一次例行的金矿搜寻中 发现了这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Disa detected it during a routine gold-seaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.75,0:32:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一种新矿石\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A new ore.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.29,0:33:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比丝轻 比铁硬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lighter than silk, harder than iron,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.58,0:33:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用作武器 它比我们最引以为豪的兵刃还要锋利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as weaponry, it would best our proudest blades.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.66,0:33:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为实物 它可能比黄金还珍贵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As specie, it might be dearer than gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.70,0:33:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它反射光线的方式很奇特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is strange how it catches the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.95,0:33:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像矿石内部就在发光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Almost seems lit from within.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.79,0:33:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说 这可能是我们矮人新时代的开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I tell you, this could be the beginning of a new era for our people.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.00,0:33:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量、繁荣…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Strength, prosperity...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.75,0:33:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么要藏着掖着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then why all the secrecy?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.12,0:33:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不庆祝一番呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why not celebrate this?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.04,0:33:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种矿的开采非常危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's perilous to mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.58,0:33:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父亲打着谨慎的名义\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My father has restricted our every efforts
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.00,0:33:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处处限制我们开采\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in the name of caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.54,0:33:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能看看吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.33,0:33:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么称呼这种神奇的矿石\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you call this miracle ore?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.29,0:33:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们的语言里 叫“灰色的闪光”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In our tongue, "gray glitter."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.37,0:33:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你们的话 可能叫什么“米银”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In yours, something like mith-raud.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.66,0:34:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不 是秘银\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no. It would be... mithril.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.54,0:34:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你远道而来 就只为了埃瑞吉安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you really did come all this way just for Eregion?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.04,0:34:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来这里是因为 20年不见老朋友一面 太久了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I came because 20 years is far too long to stay away.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.00,0:34:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我这个精灵都觉得久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even for an Elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.66,0:34:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收下吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.54,0:34:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,象征着我们的友谊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Token of our friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.25,0:34:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.45,0:34:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都林 不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No! Durin! Durin! Durin, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.95,0:34:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面有四个矮人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's four Dwarves down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.66,0:34:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Durin!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.33,0:35:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃雅瑞恩 扫地 洗高脚杯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}E?rien, floors and goblets.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.66,0:35:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.87,0:35:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 说真的 没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all right. It's all right. It's... It's... It's all right, honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.00,0:35:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你只擅长制图呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And here I thought your talents ended at draftsmanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.83,0:35:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擦擦洗洗会让人更加灵巧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Scrubbing is good for dexterity.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.70,0:35:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会长是这么说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or so the guild master says.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.75,0:35:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看这样如何  我擦地板 你洗高脚杯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, how about this? I'll do the floors, you do the goblets.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.79,0:35:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁擦得慢 晚餐钱就由谁来付\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the last one to finish pays for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.75,0:35:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不和不认识的年轻男士约会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not in the habit of going off with strange young men.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.83,0:35:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很明智 如果我看到 哪个男士举止怪异 立马告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Very wise. If I see any, you'll be the first to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.25,0:36:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管我很佩服你 每次遇到困难都会冲锋陷阵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As much as I admire your habit of charging at every obstacle in your path,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.00,0:36:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像一匹全速奔跑的小马…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}like a colt in full gallop...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.58,0:36:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你有没有想过 你不是在和食人妖或奥克作斗争\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Has it ever occurred to you that you're not battling trolls or Orcs,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.91,0:36:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是和人类\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but Men?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.37,0:36:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是真的要给我兵法方面的建议吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you really about to advise me in the art of war?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.12,0:36:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.66,0:36:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不敢 但是…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wouldn't dare. But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.79,0:36:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王的王宫 和你平日的战场并不相同 没错吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The queen's court isn't exactly your usual battlefield, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.08,0:36:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.66,0:36:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种情况下 依我看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In an instance like this, it seems to me
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.75,0:36:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好要弄清楚对手最害怕的是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that you'd do well to identify what it is that your opponent most fears.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.75,0:36:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-然后利用这一点  -不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-And exploit it? -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.08,0:36:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要给他们一种掌控这种恐惧的方法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give them a means of mastering it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.79,0:37:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样你就可以掌控对手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So that you can master them.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.45,0:37:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以按照你的标准 我在这个牢房\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So by your standards, I'm in this cell,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.66,0:37:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为我还没有找出 女王最害怕什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because I've yet to identify what the queen most fears?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.20,0:37:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只达到了低标准 但没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My very low standards. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.95,0:37:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只见了女王一小会儿 看来你已经确定了她最害怕什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I suppose you did, having met her for all of a few moments?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.75,0:37:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会面期间 你索要了船只 侮辱了她的人民、违抗了她的命令\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}During which you managed to demand a ship, insult her people, defy her orders,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.58,0:37:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这些都没有让她情绪起伏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}none of which quickened her pulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.33,0:37:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 突然间 她把你扔进了牢房\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, all of a sudden, she throws you in a cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.12,0:37:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.33,0:37:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我请求她为你的人民而战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I asked her to fight for your people.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.62,0:37:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这不是引起她愤怒的原因吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But that wasn't what provoked her anger, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.33,0:37:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要求和她父亲会面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I demanded to speak with her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.00,0:37:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多年来 没有人见过的 塔中的国王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The king in the tower, whom no one has seen in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.87,0:37:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你知道停止奔跑 给自己 一点时间思考 会发生什么了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See what happens when you stop galloping and you give yourself a moment to think?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.54,0:37:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再把我比作一匹马了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cease comparing me to a horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.25,0:37:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为交换 那你别再说服我离开这座岛了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cease trying to convince me to leave this island an you have a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.20,0:37:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请注意 精灵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Salutations, Elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.70,0:37:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摄政女王做出了决定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Queen Regent has rendered her decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.37,0:38:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚 你将在武装护送下 被运回精灵的领地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are to be shipped back to the Elves under armed escort. Tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.58,0:38:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向前一步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Step forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.91,0:38:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我不建议你这样做 -我不能让她就这样离开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I wouldn't advise that. -I can't very well let her leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.08,0:38:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果知道她要去哪里的话 你肯定会放她走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-You could. If you knew exactly where she was going.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.83,0:39:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来这上面干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you doing up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.58,0:39:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚跟人约会吃饭去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had a dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.75,0:39:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.00,0:39:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的制服呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's your uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.29,0:39:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是辞职不当学员了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Resigned from the cadets, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.33,0:39:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 比这更糟糕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.83,0:39:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被开除了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You got dismissed?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.41,0:39:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害得我们几个都被开除了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Got us all dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.83,0:39:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊熙尔…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Isil...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.79,0:39:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 你赢了 现在你可以去西部了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you've won. Now you can go west.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.41,0:39:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我毁了朋友们的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just ruined my friends' lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.91,0:39:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羞辱了家门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}shamed our family name.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.29,0:39:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不配去西部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't deserve to go west.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.66,0:39:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说了 父亲不会让我带走贝雷克的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Plus, Father won't let me take Berek.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.04,0:39:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个精灵 她逃出来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's the Elf! She's escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.25,0:39:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细搜查每一个小巷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Search every alley.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.33,0:40:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 陛下 打扰了 但是我…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Apologies, Your Majesty, for the intrusion. But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.58,0:40:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已经没法再回应了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He no longer answers to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.04,0:40:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道我会来这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How did you know I would come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.95,0:40:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面有一支驻军等着护送你上船\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A garrison of troops awaits outside to escort you to your ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.83,0:40:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放聪明点 自己主动离开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You would be wise to go willingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.41,0:40:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥瑞尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Míriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.00,0:40:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥瑞尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Míriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.75,0:41:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.83,0:41:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 父亲 我在呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-It's all right, Father. I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.08,0:41:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请原谅我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.04,0:41:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道是这个情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.45,0:41:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没几个人知道 他身体恶化到了这种地步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Few know the full extent of his decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.12,0:41:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望继续瞒着所有人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should like to keep it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.79,0:41:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们俩之间就开诚布公吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then it is time for truth between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.00,0:41:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲之前忠于精灵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your father was loyal to the Elvish ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.62,0:41:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么不愿意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why are you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.20,0:41:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.87,0:41:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.45,0:41:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父亲以前对他的信念总是很克制\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My father was always restrained in his beliefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.25,0:41:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在他加冕之后 情况发生了变化\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But after his coronation, something changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.25,0:41:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他开始变得很强硬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He became strident,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.45,0:41:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宣称我们激怒了维拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}proclaiming that we'd provoked the anger of the Valar,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.20,0:41:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宣称我们必须悔改 回归往日的道路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and must repent, and return to the old ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.50,0:42:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有民众对此感到不安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There was unease.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.16,0:42:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而当我父亲宣布 计划与精灵再续友好关系时…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And when he announced plans to renew relations with the Elves...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.95,0:42:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民众造反了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The people rebelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.12,0:42:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,损失惨重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Much was lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.70,0:42:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被选中接替他的统治\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was chosen to rule in his stead,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.20,0:42:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承诺要平息动乱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with a promise to quell the storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.70,0:42:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我继位的第一个晚上 等努门诺尔人都睡着了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But that first night, as all Númenor slept,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.91,0:42:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲把我带到了这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he brought me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.95,0:42:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕蓝提尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Palantír.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.20,0:42:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经有七颗真知晶石\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seven Seeing Stones there once were.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.33,0:42:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他六颗丢的丢 藏的藏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The other six either lost or hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.91,0:42:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一颗传给了我父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This one was passed to my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.79,0:42:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它有一个秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And with it, a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.58,0:42:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你的手放在上面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Place your hand upon it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.58,0:42:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我得警告你… -我以前触摸过帕蓝提尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I must warn you... -I have touched palantíri before.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.75,0:42:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你没有碰过这一颗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you have not touched this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.87,0:43:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才看到的是努门诺尔的未来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is Númenor's future you saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.83,0:43:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕蓝提尔能呈现出很多异象\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Palantíri show many visions.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.75,0:43:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有些异象永远不会发生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some that will never come to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.83,0:43:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它已经发生了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It has already come to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.50,0:43:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自打你来到这里 这个异象就开始了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The vision begins with your arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.33,0:43:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为我会导致努门诺尔的覆灭吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you believe I will bring about Númenor's downfall?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.41,0:43:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有努门诺尔才能让自己覆灭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only Númenor can bring about her downfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.25,0:43:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一个恩德圆满的日子 维拉将这座岛屿赐予了我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Valar gifted us this isle in a day of virtue.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.16,0:43:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倘若我们调头走向黑暗 那他们大可把这座岛屿收回\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They can take it away should we turn to the paths of darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.87,0:44:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所说的恩德 就是你祖先对精灵的忠诚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The virtue you speak of was your ancestors' loyalty to the Elves.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.91,0:44:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父亲对此深信不疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My father believed that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.91,0:44:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而他带领的路差点让我们毁于一旦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His path nearly destroyed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.50,0:44:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是为什么 明天我要宣布你已经走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is why, tomorrow, I will announce that you are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.79,0:44:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时宣布这场危机结束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And this crisis ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.20,0:44:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果对中洲 正在崛起的邪恶势力放任不管\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If the evil rising in Middle-earth is left unchecked,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.25,0:44:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那它必然扩散 毁灭我们所有人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it will spread and take us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.41,0:44:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刻意避免这场战争 可能恰恰就是导致你们覆灭的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Avoiding this war may be the very thing that brings about your downfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.91,0:44:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会质疑诸神 这就是我最后的决定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will not second-guess the gods. My decision is final.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.16,0:44:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是出于恐惧而做的决定吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A decision based in fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.79,0:44:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道作为唯一知情的人 是什么样的感受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know what it is to be the only one,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.37,0:44:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有自己能看到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the only one who sees,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.95,0:44:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有自己才知情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the only one who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.04,0:44:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我们俩 都不必再独自承担这个负担了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps neither of us have to bear that burden alone any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.25,0:44:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我求你了 弥瑞尔 不要选择恐惧的那条道路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I beg of you, Míriel, choose not the path of fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.66,0:44:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要选择充满信念的那条路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but that of faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.87,0:44:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我站在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stand with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.12,0:45:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让努门诺尔再次与精灵并肩作战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let Númenor fight alongside the Elves once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.95,0:45:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内心可以遵从信念 加拉德瑞尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Faith may bind one heart, Galadriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.16,0:45:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要让一个王国只依靠信念 实在是有点靠不住\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it is too fine a thread from which to hang a kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.25,0:45:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.16,0:45:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,树林都是光秃秃的 动物也都四散逃走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Woods are all bare. Animals are all fled.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.16,0:45:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你的孩子比我们原以为的更聪明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seems your boy had more sense than we allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.83,0:45:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门口有人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-There's someone at the gates!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.50,0:45:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.83,0:45:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-别挡路 退后  -让这小伙子过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Move out of the way. Stand back! -Let the lad through!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.37,0:45:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多吃的 慢点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's plenty. Slow down!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.20,0:45:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗恩 希奥在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rowan! Where's Theo?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.54,0:45:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他刚才说会紧跟着我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He said he'd be right behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.20,0:46:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好饿  -别推了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I'm so hungry! -Stop pushing!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.54,0:46:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她推我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She pushed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.37,0:46:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们把每个角落都检查过了 他没回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've turned over every stone. He ain't back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.33,0:46:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.70,0:46:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.45,0:46:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.54,0:46:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.29,0:46:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细搜查 不留死角\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Leave no stone unturned.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.66,0:46:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是找不到他 老大会活剥了我们的皮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Boss will skin us alive if we don't find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.37,0:46:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是老大最先把他弄丢的啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Boss is the one who lost him in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.25,0:46:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我闻到他的气味了…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Izm?mbogh...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.45,0:46:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.50,0:46:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快搜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kishdibatoth! Kishdibatoth.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.29,0:47:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快搜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kishdibatoth.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.33,0:47:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他找出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.00,0:47:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothin' here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.91,0:47:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那边 看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Over there! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.16,0:48:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鲜肉 你急着要跑去哪儿啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Going somewhere, young blood, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.16,0:48:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把剑在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.33,0:48:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.41,0:48:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从哪儿弄到的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where have you got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.66,0:48:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砍掉你一只手臂 看你开不开口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe losing your arm will loosen your lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.04,0:48:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作快点 小伙子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Swiftly, lad. -Over there! Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.00,0:48:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They are coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.33,0:48:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.79,0:49:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.29,0:49:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.95,0:49:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布隆温\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bronwyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.83,0:49:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑 去空地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Run! Get to the clearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.12,0:52:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才这是干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.87,0:52:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在恳求岩石\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was a plea to the rocks
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.58,0:52:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请它保佑矿工还有呼吸 能够安全逃生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to release the bodies of the miners with breath still inside them.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.00,0:52:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在想 要不是你去矿井找他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I cannot stop thinking that if you'd not gone down there,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.12,0:52:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都林很有可能会在那个竖井里…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Durin might have been in that shaft when it...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.37,0:52:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.16,0:52:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我骗了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry I lied to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.75,0:52:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不告诉我也是为了都林好 我们只要记住这个就可以了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were faithful to my friend. -That is all we need remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.54,0:52:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们刚把最后一名矿工拖了出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They just pulled out the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.41,0:52:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着 他们都活着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Alive. All of them alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.33,0:52:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲肯定松了一口气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your father must be so relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.33,0:52:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他把矿井关停了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He shut it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.20,0:52:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整条矿脉都要被封死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The whole vein is to be sealed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.20,0:52:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-整条矿脉  -一整条\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-The whole vein? -All of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.04,0:53:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给他点时间嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give him time.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.50,0:53:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脾气再大 气也总会消的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even the hottest coals eventually cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.08,0:53:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 但有时候 我倒是希望他一直在气头上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, but sometimes I wish they wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.75,0:53:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时候我真希望 能告诉父亲我对他的真实看法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sometimes I wish I could tell him exactly what I think of him,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.37,0:53:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再也不和那个糟老头子说话了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and never trade words with the old goat again!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.25,0:53:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父亲曾经独自航行到维林诺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My father single-handedly sailed to Valinor,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.25,0:53:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说服维拉加入战争 并成功消灭魔苟斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and convinced the Valar to join the war and vanquish Morgoth.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.16,0:53:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的事迹如此伟大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So great were his deeds
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.29,0:53:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以至于维拉 把他带到了这个世界的边界之外…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that the Valar lifted him beyond the bounds of this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.62,0:54:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远带着暮色之星划过天空\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To forever carry the Evening Star across the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.66,0:54:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么多年来 每到深夜 我都会抬头看看它…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For many years, at day's end, I would look up at it...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.16,0:54:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道如果他在看着我 他会怎么想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wondering what might he think if he were watching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.12,0:54:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会为我在他的传承之上 取得的成就而感到骄傲吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Would he be proud of what I've accomplished with his legacy?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.70,0:54:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是会因为我未能达到 他的种种期望而对我感到失望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or disappointed by the countless ways I'd failed to live up to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.25,0:54:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但后来有一天晚上 我突然想到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But then, one night, it struck me
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.12,0:54:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能听到他的评价 无论好坏 我都能心满意足\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that I would be only too happy to hear any judgment,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.16,0:54:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只求获得再次与父亲说话的机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so long as it granted me the opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.50,0:54:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕只有一次也好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to have but one more conversation with my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.83,0:54:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要浪费你和父亲所剩不多的时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do not waste what time you have left with yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.66,0:55:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃尔隆德 我期待你能解答一些问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elrond, I was hopeful you might be able to settle something.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.66,0:55:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我老公是怎么认识的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How is it that you and my husband met?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.25,0:55:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉过你 我把他从山岭食人妖手中救了出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I told you, I saved him from a hill-troll.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.91,0:55:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是两个山岭食人妖哦 -两个 对 我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Two of 'em. -Two of 'em. Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.79,0:55:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在问埃尔隆德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was asking Elrond.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.75,0:55:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那恐怕我别无选择 只能纠正一下你丈夫的描述\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then I fear I have no choice but to amend your husband's account.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.83,0:55:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时有三个山岭食人妖 而且是我救的他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There were three trolls. And it was I who saved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.66,0:55:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不照照镜子看看自己长什么样子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You wouldn't remember your face if you were gazing in a mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.16,0:55:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时我在森林里遇见他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I came upon him in the forest,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.00,0:55:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他正在躲避山岭食人妖的槌击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he was in the midst of dodging their mallet blows.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.54,0:55:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就在那里嚎啕大哭什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Wailing and screaming and such. 
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.29,0:55:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那是战场的呐喊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-It was a battle cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.58,0:55:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的喊叫声非常尖锐 我当时还以为是个小孩 我拿着弓…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The screams were so high-pitched, I thought it was a child. So I took up my bow...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.33,0:55:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是一把剑 -是一把弓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Uh, it was a sword. -It was a bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.95,0:55:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不 是一把剑  -不管怎么样…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Nah! It was a sword! -Regardless...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.50,0:55:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原谅我 父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forgive me, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.54,0:55:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太过骄傲、固执 我错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was proud and stubborn and I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.66,0:55:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不能看我一眼吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you not even look at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.20,0:56:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们矮人相信…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our people believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.70,0:56:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当新的矮人国王加冕时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That when a new Dwarf-king is crowned,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.66,0:56:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有祖先的声音都会汇集在他心头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the voices of all his forebearers flow into him,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.41,0:56:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与他分享前辈们的经验\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}sharing with him their counsel
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.58,0:56:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及智慧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.75,0:56:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至还有错误\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Even their mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.08,0:56:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.58,0:56:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不必等到那一天 就能听到我的声音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You need not wait for that day to hear my voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.58,0:56:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 儿子 我永远和你在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For, ever am I with you, my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.83,0:57:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便我非常愤怒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even in anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.87,0:57:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的时候 我基本上一直在发怒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sometimes, in anger most of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.45,0:57:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没什么需要我原谅的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is nothing to forgive.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.50,0:57:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃尔隆德邀请我明天和他一起去林顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elrond has invited me to go with him to Lindon tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.29,0:57:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该接受吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shall I accept?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.54,0:57:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃尔隆德保证 吉尔加拉德派他来这里并没有恶意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elrond has been very convincing in his assurances
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.45,0:57:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃尔隆德的话让人非常信服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that Gil-galad bore no ill intent when he sent him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.87,0:57:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 的确是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Aye. He has.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.29,0:57:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但直觉是一种强有力的辅助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But intuition's a powerful tonic.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.04,0:57:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的直觉如何\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What does yours tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.79,0:57:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉事有蹊跷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is something more at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.91,0:58:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好样的 儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good, my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.04,0:58:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.04,0:58:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去林顿吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go to Lindon.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.79,0:58:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Find out what.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.91,0:58:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.00,0:58:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 出什么事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.95,0:58:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的指挥官让我带回来一条口信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have a message. From the one who commands our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.08,0:58:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的人民要想保全性命 必须放弃这些土地的所有权…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That your people may live if you forsake all claim to these lands...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.66,0:58:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并向他宣誓效忠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And swear fealty to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.50,0:58:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们拒绝呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if we refuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.41,0:58:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他就会来欧斯提力斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's coming for Ostirith.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.04,0:59:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.87,0:59:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我说 你的所做作为 配得上喝一口好酒作为奖赏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you ask me, you deserve a nip of mash after what you done.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.50,0:59:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 拿着吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go on, take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.58,0:59:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你从我谷仓里 拿走了那把剑一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just like you took that hilt from me barn.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.25,0:59:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你说什么...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh... I don't know what...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.54,1:00:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别装了 小伙子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come off it, lad.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.75,1:00:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我说的是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know of what I speak.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.08,1:00:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道这是什么吗 这并不是剑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you know what it is? It is no sword.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.16,1:00:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是一种力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is a power.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.29,1:00:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由他的主人亲手为我们的祖先打造\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fashioned for our ancestors by his master's own hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.29,1:00:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个漂亮的仆人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A beautiful servant.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.91,1:00:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他曾经不知所踪 但终将归来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He who was lost, but shall return.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.04,1:00:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伙子 你听说过他吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you heard of him, lad?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.75,1:00:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听说过索隆吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you heard of Sauron?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.91,1:00:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定在天上看到过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You must have seen it in the skies.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.87,1:00:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几周前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A few weeks back now.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.54,1:00:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星陨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The starfall.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.87,1:00:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这意味着他的时间快到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It means his time is near.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.83,1:00:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伙子 这需要你和我共同做好准备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And it is to you and me, lad, to be ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.75,1:00:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ready for what?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.20,1:00:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静点 小伙子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hush now, lad.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.41,1:01:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你保存好体力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You save your strength.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.58,1:01:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来要发生的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'll need it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.62,1:01:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会非常消耗体力的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For what's coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.83,1:01:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lord-father...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.12,1:01:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们找到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We found it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.37,1:01:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那座塔里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's in the tower.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.45,1:01:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安心去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go in peace.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.79,1:02:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的人民会感到宽慰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your people will be relieved.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.37,1:02:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们很快就会聚集在王宫里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They will be gathering soon in the court,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.54,1:02:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚集在广场上 聆听你的宣告\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and in the plaza, to hear your announcement.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.20,1:02:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就别让他们久等了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then we ought not to keep them.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.79,1:04:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忠贞派相信 白树的花瓣落下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The faithful believe that when the petals of the White Tree fall
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.20,1:04:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是重要的预兆…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it is no idle thing,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.08,1:04:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是维拉的眼泪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but the very tears of the Valar themselves,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.37,1:04:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲜活地提醒着我们 他们时刻紧盯我们 审判我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a living reminder that their eyes and their judgment are ever upon us.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.45,1:04:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 人类命运迎来了 一个决定性的时刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is a fateful hour in the destinies of men.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.54,1:04:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个审判的时刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An hour of judgment
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.00,1:04:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这之中 我们所有人、每个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in which each of us, every one,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.00,1:04:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都必须决定自己将要成为谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}must decide who we shall be.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.20,1:04:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的心会像 小岛周围的石像一样铁石心肠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are our hearts become as the statues that surround our isle?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.95,1:04:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是会同石像雕刻的 英雄一般充满满腔热忱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or do they yet beat with the blood of the heroes that carved them?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.16,1:04:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的勇气 是否只存在于父辈的坟墓之中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is our valor confined to the graves of our slumbering fathers?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.50,1:04:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说就在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or is it here,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.79,1:04:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在我们众人之中…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}amongst us even now...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.00,1:05:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待随着太阳升起而迸发\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Waiting to burst forth as the rising Sun?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.45,1:05:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你们去面对 连我自己都不敢直面的危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would neither command, nor invite you to any danger I myself would not face.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.54,1:05:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我决定亲自护送精灵返回中洲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And so, I've decided to personally escort the Elf back to Middle-earth.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.62,1:05:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援助被围困在南方大地的凡人同胞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To aid our mortal brethren who are now besieged in the Southlands.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.16,1:05:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王已经明确表明意图\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your queen has laid bare her intent.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.29,1:05:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的船队将在十天后启程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our ships will depart in ten days.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.70,1:05:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远征军将由努门诺尔全境\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The expeditionary force will be made up of brave sons and daughters
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.33,1:05:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇敢的儿女组成\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}from across fair Númenor.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.37,1:05:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谁愿意真心实意 保护我们的摄政女王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who is willing to commit themselves to our Queen Regent's protection?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.83,1:06:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请向前一步让大家看到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Step forward and make yourself known.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.16,1:06:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愿意出征\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will serve.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.91,1:06:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愿意出征\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will serve.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.12,1:06:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愿意出征\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will serve.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.66,1:06:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愿意出征\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will serve!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.91,1:06:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愿意出征\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will serve!
